OL,3,CSigned Paul McCartney book found in
OL,4,Ccharity shop sells for nearly #1,000
OL,6,FA book signed by Paul McCartney that
OL,7,Fwas discovered at a charity shop has
OL,8,Fsold for almost #1,000.
OL,10,FThe book was donated as part of a
OL,11,Fcollection of 1970s memorabilia to an
OL,12,FOxfam shop in Aberystwyth, Ceredigion.
OL,14,FBut it was not until it had been put
OL,15,Fout for sale that staff at the charity
OL,16,Fshop discovered it held a very famous
OL,17,Fsignature inside the cover.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
