OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782906493
OL,3,CSigned Paul McCartney book found in
OL,4,Ccharity shop sells for nearly #1,000
OL,6,FThe book titled 'Paul McCartney In His
OL,7,FOwn Words' contained various
OL,8,Finterviews with The Beatles star and
OL,9,Fhad been "sitting on a shelf for a few
OL,10,Fmonths" according to the shop's
OL,11,Fmanager, Joan Randle.
OL,13,FTo Ms Randle's surprise, the book had
OL,14,Fa hidden signature just inside the
OL,15,Ffront cover, where Mr McCartney had
OL,16,Falso signed: "All the best! To ye!".
OL,26,@qD@JOUrD@GO]xD@NOUxD@cO]
