PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782906493
OL,3,CSigned Paul McCartney book found in
OL,4,Ccharity shop sells for nearly #1,000
OL,6,FThe shop worker revealed that she had
OL,7,Funcovered the gem whilst designing a
OL,8,Fwindow display and said the book
OL,9,F"wasn't something (they'd) paid
OL,10,Fparticular attention to at first".
OL,12,FShe explained: "One afternoon I found
OL,13,Fmyself with a bit of spare time and
OL,14,Fdecided to work my way through the
OL,15,Fpile. It was one of the very last
OL,16,Fthings I looked at.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@SpmqD@ZpnrD@aO]tD@POU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
