PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782906493
OL,3,CSigned Paul McCartney book found in
OL,4,Ccharity shop sells for nearly #1,000
OL,6,F"When I opened the book and saw Paul
OL,7,FMcCartney's signature, I could hardly
OL,8,Fbelieve it... It was one of the best
OL,9,Fmoments of my 10 years working in the
OL,10,Fshop."
OL,12,FThe book was sold at auction with
OL,13,FBonhams, raising #950 for Oxfam.
OL,15,FThe charity have announced that they
OL,16,Fare yet to find the donor but a
OL,17,Fspokespe
OL,19,Frson said: "This is a fantastic
OL,20,Fexample of how a single donation can
OL,21,Fmake a real difference."
OL,26,@nD@AOU{D@LOU
