OL,3,CSigned Paul McCartney book found in
OL,4,Ccharity shop sells for nearly #1,000
OL,6,FThey then go on to say: "Whether it's
OL,7,Fa signed collectible, a well-loved
OL,8,Fbook or an everyday item, every
OL,9,Fdonation and every sale helps us stand
OL,10,Fwith people when they need it most."
